    line-height: 1.6;"><p>Title: The Bittersweet Night</p>
<p>On a moonlit night in Gotham City, Batman found himself perched on a rooftop, scanning the city for any signs of chaos or crimes in progress. As the Dark Knight shifted his gaze, he noticed an unexpected silhouette in the distance. Selina Kyle, aka Catwoman, slinked into view. But something seemed off about her – an unusual sway in her hips and a wicked grin that seemed unnatural.</p>
