<p>In the last vestiges of his consciousness, Batman writhed as violent spasms of both pleasure and pain coursed through him, his ultimate release clouded with heartache and betrayal. And in the final throes of his pleasure, buttressed by a loss of air, Batman succumbed to the sweet oblivion of unconsciousness.</p></div>

