    line-height: 1.6;">I saw a video where mrbeast was helping a tiny remote island with only 250 people get internet and electricity.<br/>I was wondering. how much damage it would do if you just inflated their economy? since I doubt they make that many payemnts to external places and I dont exactly know what currency they use but they do have paper currency</div><br/><br/>LLM response:<br/><div style="
    background-color: #fff3e6;
